Cash Flow Statement
For the period: ${reportStartDate} to ${reportEndDate}
Report Generated: ${reportDate}

**Cash flows from operating activities:**
Net Income: ${netIncome}
Adjustments to reconcile net income to net cash provided by operating activities:
<jx:forEach items="${operatingActivitiesItems}" var="item" >
  ${item.name}: ${item.amount}
</jx:forEach>
Net cash provided by (used in) operating activities: ${cashFromOperations}

**Cash flows from investing activities:**
<jx:forEach items="${investingActivitiesItems}" var="item" >
  ${item.name}: ${item.amount}
</jx:forEach>
Net cash provided by (used in) investing activities: ${cashFromInvesting}

**Cash flows from financing activities:**
<jx:forEach items="${financingActivitiesItems}" var="item" >
  ${item.name}: ${item.amount}
</jx:forEach>
Net cash provided by (used in) financing activities: ${cashFromFinancing}

Net increase (decrease) in cash and cash equivalents: ${netChangeInCash}
Cash and cash equivalents at beginning of period: ${cashAtBeginningOfPeriod}
Cash and cash equivalents at end of period: ${cashAtEndOfPeriod}

**Reconciliation Check:**
Calculated Net Change in Cash: ${netChangeInCashCalculated}
Actual Net Change in Cash (End - Beginning): ${netChangeInCashActual}
Discrepancy: ${discrepancy}
